        <li>Translate the website using <a href="https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=&sl=nl&tl=en&u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuurtbudgetsno.amsterdam.nl%2F">Google Translate</a>. It’s not perfect but a pretty decent translation!</li>
    </ul>
